    <div class="contact-container">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <div class="contact-header">
                <h2>Kontaktirajte nas</h2>
                <p>GymPass - Fitness kartica dostupna za teretane i fitness objekte širom regiona.</p>
            </div>
    
            <div class="contact-details">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:kontakt@gympass.ba">kontakt@gympass.ba</a></p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                    <p><strong>Telefon:</strong> <a href="tel:+387033867591">033 867 591</a></p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    <p><strong>Adresa:</strong> Space Office Center, Pijacna 14k, Sarajevo</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    <p><strong>Radno vrijeme:</strong> Ponedjeljak - Petak: 09:00 - 17:00</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="contact-form">
            <h3>Pišite nam</h3>
            <p>Popunite kontakt formu ispod i neko iz našeg tima će Vam se javiti u najkraćem mogućem roku.</p>
            
            <form action="#" method="POST">
                <label for="name">Ime i prezime *</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
    
                <label for="email">E-mail adresa *</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
    
                <label for="company">Kompanija</label>
                <input type="text" id="company" name="company">
    
                <label for="phone">Broj telefona</label>
                <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
    
                <label for="message">Vaša poruka *</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
    
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Pošaljite</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>














    
